1.0.0.readme:
# Seafoam Pastel Theme

A dark syntax theme for Atom, ported from [https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes#seafoam-pastel](https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes#seafoam-pastel).  

[![dark][3]][4]  

[3]: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/unforswearing/seafoam-pastel-theme/master/Seafoam-Pastel-Dark-Textmate.png  

[4]: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/unforswearing/seafoam-pastel-theme/master/Seafoam-Pastel-Dark-Textmate.png  

(images shown using [source code pro](https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-code-pro))
